	<key>readme</key>
	<string>## Setup

Set the ServiceNow subdomain in the Workflow's Configuration (e.g. `google` for `google.service-now.com`).

## Usage

Open any ServiceNow ticket directly in your browser via the `snow` keyword.

![Opening a ServiceNow ticket with the snow keyword](images/snow.png)

* &lt;kbd&gt;↩&lt;/kbd&gt; Open ticket in default browser.

Supported ticket types: RITM, CHG, DMND, ENHC, INC, SNSVC.

Alternatively, use a dedicated keyword for each ticket type via the `ritm`, `chg`, `dmnd`, `enhc`, `inc`, and `snsvc` keywords.

![Opening a RITM ticket with the dedicated keyword](images/ritm.png)

All keywords are configurable in the Workflow's Configuration.
</string>
